#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pivot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.pivot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:1 of
msgid "Return reshaped DataFrame organized by given index / column values."
msgstr "返回按给定索引/列值组织的重塑 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:3 of
msgid ""
"Reshape data (produce a \"pivot\" table) based on column values. Uses "
"unique values from specified `index` / `columns` to form axes of the "
"resulting DataFrame. This function does not support data aggregation, "
"multiple values will result in a MultiIndex in the columns. See the "
":ref:`User Guide <reshaping>` for more on reshaping."
msgstr ""
"根据列值重塑数据（生成“透视”表）。使用指定 `index` / `columns` 的唯一"
"值来构成结果 DataFrame 的轴。此函数不支持数据聚合，多个值将导致列中出现 "
"MultiIndex。有关重塑的更多信息，请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <reshaping>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:9 of
msgid "Column to use to make new frame's index. If None, uses existing index."
msgstr "用于创建新框架索引的列。如果为 None，则使用现有索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:12 of
msgid "Column to use to make new frame's columns."
msgstr "用于创建新框架列的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:14 of
msgid ""
"Column(s) to use for populating new frame's values. If not specified, all"
" remaining columns will be used and the result will have hierarchically "
"indexed columns."
msgstr ""
"用于填充新框架值的列。如果未指定，则使用所有剩余列，并且结果将具有层次"
"索引列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:19 of
msgid "Returns reshaped DataFrame."
msgstr "返回重塑后的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:22 of
msgid ""
"When there are any `index`, `columns` combinations with multiple     "
"values. `DataFrame.pivot_table` when you need to aggregate."
msgstr ""
"当存在任何具有多个值的 `index`、`columns` 组合时。如果需要聚合，请使用 `"
"DataFrame.pivot_table`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.pivot_table`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:27 of
msgid ""
"Generalization of pivot that can handle duplicate values for one "
"index/column pair."
msgstr "透视表的泛化形式，可以处理一个索引/列对的重复值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.unstack`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:30 of
msgid "Pivot based on the index values instead of a column."
msgstr "基于索引值而不是列进行透视。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`wide_to_long`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:33 of
msgid "Wide panel to long format. Less flexible but more user-friendly than melt."
msgstr "宽格式面板转为长格式。比 melt 更少灵活性但更友好。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:36 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:37 of
msgid ""
"For finer-tuned control, see hierarchical indexing documentation along "
"with the related stack/unstack methods."
msgstr "如需更精细的控制，请参阅层次索引文档以及相关的 stack/unstack 方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:41 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:70 of
msgid "You could also assign a list of column names or a list of index names."
msgstr "也可以分配一个列名列表或一个索引名列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:102 of
msgid "A ValueError is raised if there are any duplicates."
msgstr "如果存在任何重复项，则会引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.pivot.pivot:114 of
msgid ""
"Notice that the first two rows are the same for our `index` and `columns`"
" arguments."
msgstr "注意，对于我们的 `index` 和 `columns` 参数来说，前两行是相同的。"

